Kristina Karo is suing Mila Kunis for $5,000 . 
  She claims the actress stole her chicken when she was seven years old . 
  The actress and her fiance Ashton Kutcher responded to the lawsuit with a video claiming she will counter-sue for injuries sustained while watching her music video . 
  Karo claims she suffered emotional trauma when a seven-year-old Kunis stole her pet hen . 
  She says she was a classmate of Kunis in Ukraine and that she was 'envious' of the chicken . 
  She is suing Kunis because she claims she was forced to watch the video . 
 